name: Polish Banknotes image classifier
description: Identify the most prominent object in the image from a set of 7 categories.

input_tensor_metadata.name: image
input_tensor_metadata.description: Input image to be classified. The expected image is 128 x 128, with three channels (red, blue, and green) per pixel. Each value in the tensor is a single byte between 0.0 and 1.0.

associated_files.name: labels.txt
associated_files.description: Labels for objects that the model can recognize.
